### Safe read-only checks for Fulfillment API.

@FulfillmentApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5006

@shipmentId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000


### Health check
GET {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/health


### List shipments
GET {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/shipments


### Get shipment by id
GET {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/shipments/{{shipmentId}}


### Missing shipment should return 404
GET {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/shipments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
